paragraphs.title: Q1 How many startups are there in Pune City?

paragraphs.text: spark.sql("select Startup_Name from ind where City='Pune'").distinct().count()
spark.sql("select Startup_Name from ind where City='Pune'").count()

paragraphs.title: How many startups in Pune got their Seed/ Angel Funding?
paragraphs.text: spark.sql("select Startup_Name from ind where City='Pune'and InvestmentnType in('Seed Funding','Angel Funding') ").count()

paragraphs.title: What is the total amount raised by startups in Pune City? Hint - use regex_replace to get rid of null
paragraphs.text: spark.sql("select sum(Amount_in_USD) from ind where City='Pune'").show()
